abstract.para: The information in this guide is essential to individuals and groups participating in the development of the System for Population Kinetics (SPK), an open source project of the RFPK Laboratory of the &dept; of the &uw;. RFPK's work is supported, in part, by grant P41 EB-001975 of the National Institutes of Health (NIH) of the U.S. Department of Health and Human Services.
